# Initiators 

Data from an external system is received by and endpoint and sent to the router 
where a bespoke flow is performed.  

## Flow Initiation Message Construction 
Once data is recieved from the endpoint the connector must construct a *Flow Initiation Message* 
and send that message to the router exchange to initiate the flow

The message below will make a WSG request to get items, if any items are found they 
are used to initiate the flow.

```


{
  "accountId": "acct1",
  "routeAction": "ROUTE",
  "wfdSessionId": "eventId-GUID",
  "eventId": "eventId-GUID",
  "eventDateTime": "20170205T23:25:32.000+0000",
  "eventType": "WSG_GET_ITEM_REQUEST",
  "eventSource": "SCHEDULER",
  "flowContext": {
    "testProdFlag": "TEST",
    "altBillingAccount": "acct999"
  },
  "payloadAttachments": [
    {
      "fileName": "dummy.dat",
      "fileStorageId": "storage-GUID",
      "charEncoding": "UTF-8",
      "fileType": "TXT",
      "location": "STORAGE"
    }
  ]
}


```

Here is the schemp for an initial flow message

```
{
  "$schema": "http://json-schema.org/draft-04/schema#",
  "title": "Routing Message",
  "description": "Description of an orchestrated message",
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "accountId": {
      "description": "A unique Id for the organization that owns this message.",
      "type": "string"
    },
    "routeAction": {
      "description": "ROUTE - continue an existing flow, END - end a flow.",
      "type": "string"
    },
    "wfdSessionId": {
      "description": "A globally unique ID for this run-time instance of the workflow, used for tracking.",
      "type": "string"
    },
    "eventId": {
      "description": "A globally unique ID for this event.  This will be used for tracking",
      "type": "string"
    },
    "eventDateTime": {
      "description": "The date and time on which this event occurred.",
      "type": "string"
    },
    "eventType": {
      "description": "The type of event such as ECOM_GET_ITEM, ERP_GET_ITEM, ECOM_GET_ORDER, ERP_GET_ORDER,  etc.. ",
      "type": "string"
    },
    "eventSource": {
      "description": "The name of the event producer, WSG, ROUTER, TX, etc...",
      "type": "string"
    },
    "flowContext": {
      "type": "object",
      "additionalProperties": {
        "type": "string",
        "description": "string values"
      }
    },
    "payloadAttachments": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "location": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "INLINE or STORAGE, if STORAGE then fileStorageId is required, if INLINE then inlineData is required ",
            "required": true
          },
          "inlineData": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "The file data",
            "required": false
          },          
         "fileName": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "The file name",
            "required": true
          },
          "fileStorageId": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "A unique storage id used to retrieve the file if needed",
            "required": false
          },
          "charEncoding": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "the char encodeing of the file",
            "required": true
          },
          "fileType": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "file type such as, ITEMS, ORDERS, SALES ",
            "required": false
          }
        },
        "description": "the value",
        "required": true
      }
    }
  },
  "required": [
    "accountId",
    "routeAction",
    "eventId",
    "eventDateTime",
    "eventType",
    "eventSource"
  ]
}
```

